Subject: [PATCH 05/18] Complete HVP implementation for all time integrators

- Fix Crank-Nicolson HVP by adding prev_* methods for R_{n+1} contributions
- Add TimeAdjointDerivativeChecker for comprehensive validation
- Add component-level HVP tests for each time stepper
- Add PyTorch autograd comparison tests (< 1e-8 tolerance)
- Add time adjoint HVP documentation in Quarto
- Ensure base test classes excluded from test discovery
