+        For Crank-Nicolson: d²R/dy_n² = -(Δt/2)·(d²f/dy²)|_{y_n, t_n}
+
+        Note: The f(y_{n-1}) term doesn't contribute because y_{n-1} is fixed.
         """
         self._residual.set_time(self._time + self._deltat)
