From aff8a75c9aa02e7a72ed99527412ff49f04ba08d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: John Jakeman <jdjakem@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 7 Dec 2025 13:19:15 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 12/18] Add Phase 2: Cartesian meshes and affine transforms

Implements 1D, 2D, 3D Cartesian mesh classes with:
- Tensor product mesh construction from 1D node arrays
- Optional coordinate transforms (reference to physical space)
- Boundary index computation and access
- Jacobian matrix and determinant computation

Adds affine transforms (scale and translate) for all dimensions.

Note: Some tests fail due to missing zeros_like in backend - to be fixed.
