Date: Sun, 7 Dec 2025 14:12:58 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 17/18] Add Phase 6: Linear solvers with PCG and
 preconditioners

Implements direct and iterative linear solvers for spectral collocation:

- DirectSolver: wraps backend solve function for direct solution
- ConjugateGradient: standard CG for symmetric positive definite systems
- PreconditionedConjugateGradient: PCG with optional preconditioner
- JacobiPreconditioner: diagonal preconditioning
- BlockJacobiPreconditioner: block diagonal preconditioning

Features:
- Matrix-free variants (solve_matvec) for CG and PCG
- Factory functions for easy preconditioner creation
- Follows IterativeSolverProtocol and PreconditionerProtocol
- 20 new tests, 136 total tests passing in collocation module
